Jerusalem as the capital of Israel and earmarked 100 million
U.S. dollars for moving the U.S. embassy in Tel Aviv to Jerusalem.
</P>
<P>
The decision was made amid international criticism and Arab
attacks against Israeli insistence on construction of a new Jewish
settlement in Arab East Jerusalem.
</P>
<P>
The Israeli policy has caused the Middle East peace process to
a standstill and deepened Palestinian resentment in the disputed
holy city which the Palestinians are struggling to make it capital
of their future state.
</P>
