<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 15 (Xinhua) -- Indonesians took the lion's
share of the titles by winning six out of the eight titles at the
four-day Second World Dragon Boat Racing Championships which
closed here on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
