men's team to take the bronze medal in the 500 meters event of the
Mixed category.
</P>
<P>
The United States took the only other gold medal, that of the
500 meters event of the Open Class.
</P>
<P>
Germans won three silver and three bronze medals while Canada
took two silvers.
</P>
<P>
At the championships' closing ceremony today, Liu Ji, the
Chinese President of the International Dragon Boat Federation
handed the Federation flag to Mike Haslam, Chairman of the British
Dragon Boat Association and head of the organizing committee of
the 1999 world championships in Nottingham, Britain. 
