<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, June 15 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lanka's National Water supply
and Drainage Board (NWSDB) last week launched a water supply
project with the aim to provide safe drinking water to rural areas
by the year 2010, according to sources from the board today.
</P>
