<HEADLINE> Kuerten Charges Into Final Against Mantilla </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, June 14 (Xinhua) -- French Open champion Gustavo Kuerten
cruised into the final of the Bologna international clay-court
tournament with a crushing victory over Italian Marzio Martelli on
Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The 20-year old Brazilian, who is ranked 15 in the world after
shooting up from 66th place following his French Open triumph,
