</P>
<P>
Last Sunday's surprise French Open winner, who extended his
winning run to 16 matches with Saturday's victory, now faces
Spain's Felix Mantilla, who ranks just behind him at 16.
</P>
<P>
Second seed Mantilla defeated Morocco's Karim Alami 6-3,
6-2. 
</P>
</TEXT>
