<DOCNO> XIE19970615.0164 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-06-15 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Graf Considers Retire from Tennis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, June 14 (Xinhua) -- Former world number one Steffi Graf
is considering retiring from tennis, according to local reports
on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Graf said in an interview that there was no guarantee she
would resume her career following her knee operation in Vienna
this week.
</P>
<P>
The operation is expected to rule Graf out of the game for up
to six months.
</P>
<P>
Graf, who celebrated her 28th birthday on Saturday, said that
she was hopeful of the abilities of the physicians but would have
no problem ending her career.
</P>
<P>
"I am completely open on this question," Graf was quoted as
saying. 
</P>
</TEXT>
